node.text:
Our new Miscellaneous Collection!🧸🛋
This collection is a series of fun, beautiful, and incredibly hard household items. Even including our two brand mascots, Hard Willy & Hell The Hound. All pieces made by us, the Hard Jewelry team. It took a little bit more than a year to perfect each piece- and although each piece isn't perfect, it is an accurate representation of the hard jewelry experience. Hard and fun.... Pause.... Resume... I hope you enjoy🖤 

Our Miscellaneous Collection will be releasing on March 26th @ 8 p.m. MTN time🙂🖤

node.text:
I woke up today and realized there’s much more to life than just jewelry... I am going bankrupt...

See how that got your attention? My teacher always taught me I need a captivating hook for the introduction.

Anyways, I’m making this post solely to remind our haters that we are STILL shipping fast and free and always will‼️

We’re kind of like the sun. You can rely on us to bring you the heat, everyday💯

Our team is currently shipping out all orders from the weekend as I type this out.

Shoutout the HJ team man, doing God’s work.

Love you guys.

node.text:
It’s taken me a long time to get the courage to tell you all this... It’s also something I’ve been wanting to tell you for a while but just didn’t want to.

Hopefully after, we can still be friends and love eachother the same..!🖤

But,
This page isn’t just a meme page....
We sell jewelry too😞

I know this may be a surprise to most of you, and I apologize if this changes anything. I still love you, my kittens
